These files should compile on linux 2.6.17 and earlier without change.

For kernel 2.6.18 and 2.6.18.x, please apply the 2.6.18-patch.  This should be
applied in this directory using "patch -p1 < 2.6.18-patch".

For kernel 2.6.19-rcx, please apply the 2.6.19-patch.  This should be
applied in this directory using "patch -p1 < 2.6.19-patch".
